de.erichseifert.gral.data

Class DataAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.erichseifert.gral.data.DataAccessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<Comparable<?>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Column, Row

    public abstract class DataAccessor
extends Object
implements Iterable<Comparable<?>>, Serializable
    Abstract base for reading substructures of a data source, i.e. columns or rows. DataAccessors are iterable and provide utility methods for statistics and array conversion.
    See Also:
    DataSource, Serialized Form
